<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre> <p>接下来，你需要在 <code>.env</code> 文件中添加:</p> <pre class=" language-php"><code class=" language-php"><span class="token constant">TRANSLATE_TYPE</span><span class="token operator">=</span>baidu<span class="token punctuation">.</span>com
